                "name": "Eby Escobar"
            },
            "reviewBody": "Nope. I just went to Mexico City, the tour guide at Teotihuacan told us Americans have it wrong. You put the salt on the lemon/lime wedge, squeeze a bit of the juice in your mouth, hold it, take the shot, and bite into what's left of the wedge. I swear no tequila has ever gone down smoother."
        },
